Rating: 3
My husband and I enjoyed the dish .... I substituted Port Salut cheese in one version and smoked Gouda in another. Port Salut was the favorite. No added seasoning really needed. Also, grate/towel the potato right before cooking.

Rating: 3
This is really a fantastic recipe. Its tasty and very quick and easy to prepare. The potatoes definitely need a little seasoning (onion and garlic are nice additions), but the dish is a great accompaniment to many entrees. Its a nice change from regular potatoes or rice.

