Rating: 4
Very simple to make and it's a nice change of pace as a potato side dish. Used swiss cheese (didn't have gruyere on hand) and it turned out fine but I can see that gruyere would make it just that much better.

Rating: 4
This is one of my favorite potato recipes. So easy and yet so full of flavor! Goes great with a steak on the grill. We have tried other cheeses, but nothing compares with the great taste of Gruyere. If you like Gruyere, you'll love this recipe.